======= description of files
== raw/ contains raw data, see below for locations it was acquired from
== clean/ data after cleaning, generally .RData files with tms for
   lightcurves and periods
== funcs.R functions used for processing raw data
== All other files process a particular raw data set 


======= to get started, download and unzip the files below in the raw/ folder
1) stripe82candidateVar_v1.1.dat
  - file available here:
    http://www.astro.washington.edu/users/ivezic/sdss/catalogs/S82variables.html
2) AllLCs
  - directory available here:
    http://www.astro.washington.edu/users/ivezic/sdss/catalogs/S82variables.html
3) apj326724t2_mrt.txt
  - file available here:
    http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/708/1/717/suppdata/apj326724t2_mrt.txt
4) table1/
  - rrlyrae light curves provided by sesar, for unknown reason,
    includes some light curves not in AllLCS for